<i>Posted by Fistan on 06-02-02 09:15 PM:</i>

<p><b> Discussion of news item</b></p>

<p>Here's a thread for people to discuss my news item on the front LOA page. Feel free to flame, whinge, discuss, argue, etc etc.<br />
<br />
Like I said in my news item, we need more guild events together! Pick a date, pick an objective (Claim a keep, raid DF, explore an enemy frontier) and get it organised! Anybody can organise an event, it just needs thought, dedication and planning. I will be too busy for the next week, and maybe for the week after; but after then I'll get my thinking-cap on and start planning away for fun things we can do.<br />
<br />
Discuss! That's a polite request, not the harsh order it might sound like...<p><font face="verdana, arial, helvetica" size="2" >__________________<br>
<img src="http://www.kgmedia.com/uploads/greggar_sig.jpg" border="0" alt=""></font></p></p>
